  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain how to determine the equivalent capacitance of capacitors in series and in parallel combinations</item>
<item>Compute the potential difference across the plates and the charge on the plates for a capacitor in a network and determine the net capacitance of a network of capacitors</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
